{"tid":628530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬屎坑：警隊與港鐵為港人所驕傲","createTime":"2018-04-14T03:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T04:02:01.000Z","uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"da3fc86c5bb7a7639e928f5fae21252dd3200486","tid":628530,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:14:02.000Z","msg":"香港警察學院今早在黃竹坑警校舉行結業會操，有44名見習督察及283名學警結業，由港鐵非執行主席馬時亨檢閱儀式。馬時亨致詞時一再強調感謝警隊支持，並指警隊與港鐵一樣為港人所驕傲。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨在致辭時多番感謝及讚揚警隊，指市民每日乘搭港鐵，獲得舒適的搭乘環境，有賴精良警隊協助，引來全場笑聲。他又指，作為香港市民，以警隊自豪，又稱港鐵與警隊有緊密合作，設有鐵路警區，警方在青衣站設有警察控制中心，當列車發生事故，會即時作出協調及應變，警務人員亦會走入鐵路巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n馬又提及在沙中線地盤曾發現二戰時期的炸彈，感激警方爆炸品處理課兩次總動員進行拆彈任務，更點名稱讚處理課炸彈處理主任盧秉善（Adam Roberts），讚揚其表現專業、有效率及應變快速，保障了工程人員及市民的安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6701aaa0e1add166f2bd470c1a8a36dd776cc530","tid":628530,"uid":136994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"今日新鮮滾熱辣<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】柴灣警署發生警員偷妓女肉金醜聞，兩名參與掃黃的東區特別職務隊人員，在將妓女帶返警署調查期間，疑有人貪心在臨時羈留室偷走妓女手袋內3,000元，妓女其後在其他警員為其財物「打包頭」時發覺失竊，警方事後翻看閉路電視片段，揭發兩警與案有關將他們拘捕，並由港島總區重案組跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n涉監守自盜的兩名警員分別姓梁（32歲）及姓吳（31歲），前者當差8年，後者加入警隊逾9年，同駐守港島東區特別職務隊。"},{"pid":"4cf9eda59a08b596cb14d3557b0fdb9328dc1e7e","tid":628530,"uid":810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:16:05.000Z","msg":"佢係咪曲線緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b1bdc9b5b1972c2c01b4ea48a37d9c12720486","tid":628530,"uid":60668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02ffb988afc8d240afef6096e0bf5b1d81e1c07","tid":628530,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:31:40.000Z","msg":"龜鐵職員有部分執法權力（附例賦予）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0b1107887534380dd7886d707a7b6f019bb501","tid":628530,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"關佢港鐵主席咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明無官想去事旦搵個人去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8975a87b42d81ee7fcfe5fb17b28b393fa34e0a6","tid":628530,"uid":38528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"廿年前就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe03330d4c2383239c2e275e9185371219b62cbc","tid":628530,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:38:19.000Z","msg":"點解係由港鐵主席檢閱？<br />\n一個大官都無？"},{"pid":"b922e953d39f07390717fa00cc4fcd2433b98712","tid":628530,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"高層震怒"},{"pid":"555ba4095e40e5557a6c82957464e9a9dcf6bac6","tid":628530,"uid":37505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"議員、人大、政協或者D3以上過百人&hellip;<br />\n幾時輪到個地鐵主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69fd2ce6f03dc3837ea9d0ec6f448aeddf56f87","tid":628530,"uid":12001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:55:08.000Z","msg":"呢條友講親咩都比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心佢收下口<br />\n<br />\nbtw mtr入面d中高層都當自己係差人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e539ca69f952a801dc8515f8be85f52e403c7c99","tid":628530,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe03330d4c2383239c2e275e9185371219b62cbc","tid":628530,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:38:19.000Z","msg":"點解係由港鐵主席檢閱？<br />\n一個大官都無？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi